➜「风哥资讯」甘肃省鼓励陇南受灾群众搬往兰州新区、河西等地区
http://www.sohu.com/a/416768309_804243	53663
<p><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">原标题：唐仁健在陇南调研时强调：科学有序推进救灾重建慎终如始抓好脱贫攻坚</span></strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200906/fbe1fba77d8f4d3f95872dbb10726ef9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200906/5a58e21959c54e9b885ceed0a9775ebf.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200906/75f09b10612b4d78bc4f9554916dbc5c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200906/f91ef4b683dc4a118a338bce33ca6c53.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
